title: added objects and some drawables
message:
added objects and some drawables

Added Entities with a system for post-load modification as well as
allowing Entities that are "attached" to other Entities to have this
process handled by their parent. Also added some Drawable classes:
Picture, Text and TextFromJSON.

title: new asset classes
message:
new asset classes

In refactored framework, there is a distinction between Assets (loaded
data)and Objects (entities in the app). This is the new Asset classes:
one for image and another for data stored in a JSON text format.
